Package: qlcVisualize
Title: Visualization for Quantitative Language Comparison
Description: Collection of visualizations as used in quantitative
        language comparison. Currently implemented are visualisations
        dealing nominal data with multiple levels ("level map" and
        "factor map"), and assistance for making weighted geographical
        Voronoi-maps ("weighted map").
Version: 0.4
Date: 2024-07-31
